Map originally lila_panic re-made by jediwithredeye

# This map now supports 64 players
# 3D lighting added


Added extras:

3 new vent systems
panic room which locks you in
construction site
All new 3D lighting has been added
Several new rooms added
Higher towers with more access points
Unbreakable glass windows added for better barricading
Sewage tunnel drop


I have spent alot of time on this map and i hope this map is enjoyed 
by others as much as i enjoyed creating it.

Peace & have fun =)
